{"tid":574232,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！保特簽約黃衣勁旅 週二官宣加盟","createTime":"2018-02-27T08:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T08:59:17.000Z","uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cf62fabffb4e778a71c803a5cdf37b7bb9655909","tid":574232,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/02/27/2/2599da72e417d8f8aca2d11ca75a93e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F2%2F2599da72e417d8f8aca2d11ca75a93e2.jpg&h=4cb03e38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/02/27/b/b54319174f219cdc2b2c2e158296f927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2Fb%2Fb54319174f219cdc2b2c2e158296f927.jpg&h=40856679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　香港時間2月26日，南非球隊馬姆羅迪日落發表了一張照片，這是牙買加飛人保特的訓練照，看起來保特要加盟的會是這支南非球隊。<br />\n　　保特在昨天宣佈了自己完成簽約的消息，他表示自己會在格連威治時間週二8點公佈自己的下家，而馬姆羅迪日落球會也表示，他們會在同一時間公佈重大消息！<br />\n　　馬姆羅迪日落官方表示：「足球不會是一成不變的！讓我們明天8點見！」他們還配上了保特在球場的照片，這似乎也是在暗示保特將轉行開啟自己的足球生涯。"},{"pid":"886b2ae24cb89d97366a5d9a0489d6f4f344f970","tid":574232,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"屌又吹到多仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576f69b11d35a56c76a54a878346b2fde795a10c","tid":574232,"uid":46965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"都係黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fb54e1f79fdc0b3f384a0d66ff60bc8695f1d4","tid":574232,"uid":2323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"連人帶球衝入龍不是夢"},{"pid":"505d7d30fddf3deb618f9d80493b4d3145c13434","tid":574232,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201